COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xf0
STRING: Once again, I headed to where Fal would be waiting.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xfc
STRING: Before I knew it, I was on my way to the practice room.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x108
STRING: It was just fun performing with Fal.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x114
STRING: That wasn't the only feeling that was motivating me,
however.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x120
STRING: I knew just how dedicated she was to her music, and I
had also started to learn about the secret which lay
behind that dedication.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x140
STRING: And again, I stood in front of the practice room door.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x17c
STRING: [Fal] “Chris.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x192
STRING: Fal spoke without turning to look at me.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x19e
STRING: And then, she slowly turned to face me.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1ce
STRING: [Fal] “Shall we start rehearsing straight off? Or would
you like to warm up a little first?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1ee
STRING: Fal spoke naturally, just like a close friend would.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x204
STRING: The score sitting in front of her was already open to the
page that I had been having trouble with.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x21a
STRING: [Chris] “Let's just rehearse.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x230
STRING: We didn't rehearse long, nor did we rehearse that many
times.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x23c
STRING: But, we were able to make the most of our limited time
and we practiced intently, so we didn't need to
exchange many more words than this.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x252
STRING: But that may have been only in regards to music.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x302
STRING: [Fal] “Good job.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x318
STRING: [Chris] “Yeah, that was nice.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x32e
STRING: Seated at my Fortelle, I stretched my arms out, and
loosened the tension in my shoulders.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x344
STRING: That was how long we had both refused to stop
practicing.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x376
STRING: [Fal] “That might have been perfect.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x38c
STRING: Stretching out her body in the same way as I did, Fal
commented casually.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x3a2
STRING: [Chris] “You think so?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x3b8
STRING: Fal always complimented what deserved
complimenting, and pointed out what wasn't good
enough.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x3ce
STRING: But today, she didn't say any more than that.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x3f6
STRING: [Fal] “We still have some time left, shall we keep going,

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x40c
STRING: [Chris] “Either way is fine with me.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x43e
STRING: [Fal] “You're truly fine either way, huh?

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x46c
STRING: In that case...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x478
STRING: [Chris] “Y-Yeah...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x4aa
STRING: [Fal] “I'm kidding, it's a little early, but lets go home.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x4c0
STRING: [Chris] “I really did mean that I was fine with either

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x4f2
STRING: [Fal] “Aha-ha. But, too late now!

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x520
STRING: Let's clean up
and head home.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x536
STRING: [Chris] “Alright.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x59c
STRING: [Fal] “Feeling a little off today?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x5b2
STRING: [Chris] “Umm...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x5e4
STRING: [Fal] “It seemed like there was a few points where you

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x5fa
STRING: [Chris] “Sorry.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x642
STRING: [Fal] “I didn't mean it like that, I'm not trying to criticize

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x662
STRING: [Chris] “Thanks.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x694
STRING: [Fal] “I think you yourself understand which parts

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x6b4
STRING: She said this not in a half-hearted way, but in a way that

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x6ca
STRING: That, I was aware of.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x6d6
STRING: [Chris] “Sure, that works for me.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x6ec
STRING: While I checked through the individual sections of the
score that I felt weren't good enough, Fal started
chatting to me.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x728
STRING: [Fal] “We're really starting to get used to playing like
this, aren't we?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x73e
STRING: [Chris] “Yeah. It's been, what, three weeks?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x75c
STRING: [Fal] “Wow, so long already?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x772
STRING: Fal was nodding as if she was in deep contemplation.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x77e
STRING: Unlike Fal, who sang perfectly, I wasn't in a position to
be so easy going.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x794
STRING: Wanting to make up for the mistakes I made just now, I
went to sit back down at my Fortelle, but for some
reason Fal stopped me.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x7d0
STRING: [Fal] “Chris, wait a moment.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x7e6
STRING: [Chris] “Hm? Weren't we going to rehearse one more
time?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x818
STRING: [Fal] “That's what I was thinking too, but why don't we
stop here for today? Practicing all the time like this must
be tiring.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x838
STRING: [Chris] “That may be true, but...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x86a
STRING: [Fal] “It'll be fine. We've practiced so much already, so a
little break could be... You know?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x88a
STRING: [Chris] “Hrm... I suppose you could be right.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x8bc
STRING: [Fal] “Let's call it a day and go home.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x8d2
STRING: [Chris] “Alright...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x90a
STRING: [Fal] “Chris...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x920
STRING: [Chris] “Yes?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x936
STRING: I sensed a slight change in her voice.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x942
STRING: It sounded gentle, but at the same time there was
something else that dominated her tone, something
lonely or defeated.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x958
STRING: And from the words that followed, I found out that I
was not just imagining it.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x980
STRING: [Fal] “Is there something troubling you?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x996
STRING: [Chris] “...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x9b4
STRING: [Fal] “The whole time we have been practicing together,
hasn't there been something on your mind?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x9d4
STRING: [Chris] “...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x9ea
STRING: As I was unable to answer either of her questions, Fal
paused for just a few moments, and then spoke a name
I had not expected to hear.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xa1c
STRING: [Fal] “Is it because of Arietta?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xa32
STRING: [Chris] “How did you know about...?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xa50
STRING: [Fal] “Tortinita told me.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xa7e
STRING: Well... Actually, I made her tell me. I'm really sorry.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xa94
STRING: [Chris] “No... That's fine.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xab2
STRING: [Fal] “I wasn't planning on saying anything but... It
seems to be bothering you.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xad2
STRING: [Chris] “Oh... I'm sorry.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xb04
STRING: [Fal] “Don't be. It's not like I'm angry about it or
anything...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xb24
STRING: Fal quickly put on a smile, and even made the tone of
her voice cheerful again.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xb56
STRING: [Fal] “It's just that there is someone better suited to
being your partner than I am.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xb76
STRING: [Chris] “Someone... Better suited, huh...?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xb8c
STRING: Of course, I knew who she was talking about.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xb98
STRING: But, whether or not that person was better suited, I truly
did not know.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xbae
STRING: [Chris] “But... You may be right.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xbc4
STRING: There was one thing, though... What she had said
about not being a suitable partner.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xbda
STRING: It was the other way around.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xbe6
STRING: It was I who wasn't a suitable partner for Fal.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xbf2
STRING: I had half-heartedly searched for a partner, and was
leaning towards her out of guilt about Torta and Arie...

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xc08
STRING: And as a result, I'd wasted not only my own time but
also Fal's precious time.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xc1e
STRING: But, if I had said that to her, she may have tried to look
out for me and offer to continue practicing.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xc34
STRING: So instead of disagreeing with her, I chose not to cause
any more trouble for her than I already had, and
nodded.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xc66
STRING: [Fal] “It seems like you realize it too.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xc7c
STRING: [Chris] “I guess so.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xcae
STRING: [Fal] “You guess so, huh...?

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xcd4
STRING: You have a habit of saying that, apparently.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xce0
STRING: [Chris] “Apparently so. Did Torta tell you that too...?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xcf6
STRING: Answering no more of my questions, Fal turned to her
music stand and started to gather up her scores.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xd0c
STRING: I also started to do the same, and gathered up the
scores she had copied for me.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xd22
STRING: [Chris] “I should... Return this, shouldn't I?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xd54
STRING: [Fal] “No, keep it.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xd6a
STRING: [Chris] “But what about when you need to give a copy
to someone else?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xd92
STRING: [Fal] “Then, I'll just write out another one.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xda8
STRING: [Chris] “But...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xdc6
STRING: [Fal] “Take a look at it, right here.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xddc
STRING: Fal didn't take back the score she had made for me, but
instead just pointed at it.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xe0e
STRING: [Fal] “You've written notes all over it... I don't think I
could give this to anyone.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xe2e
STRING: I had rushed to write things down during our practice,
so the score was covered in various messily written
notes.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xe44
STRING: Things like “make eye contact here” for getting our
timing right, and so on.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xe50
STRING: [Chris] “Sorry...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xe82
STRING: [Fal] “Why apologize?

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xeb0
STRING: I mentioned it because it makes me happy. This is my
song, and you put all your heart into practicing it, right?
So don't apologize, just keep it.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xed0
STRING: [Chris] “Thanks.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xf22
STRING: I returned home, and talked to Phorni about what had
happened today, and then took the score out of my bag
and gazed at it one last time.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xf38
STRING: And then, I carefully placed it inside a box that
contained all the other scores and notes that I had
written in classes and the like, never to be seen again.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xfb4
STRING: I checked the clock hanging on the wall on my way out
of the building, and noticed it was over an hour and a
half earlier than the usual time I would have
finished up.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xfca
STRING: [Chris] “I guess these kinds of practice days might be
nice for a change.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1004
STRING: [Fal] “As long as we really only do this as a nice change,
otherwise we'll get sloppy.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x101a
STRING: [Chris] “Well, you're the one who suggested it.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1056
STRING: [Fal] “This is just right for me. I have a feeling that if I
left you in charge, we'd be going home at this time
everyday.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1076
STRING: [Chris] “You're so mean.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x10a8
STRING: [Fal] “Aha-ha!”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x10de
STRING: The rain had become considerably lighter today.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x10ea
STRING: There is never a day that it doesn't rain in this town, but
considering that, the rain today was especially light.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1100
STRING: So light in fact, that I could only feel it tinkling on my
skin when I concentrated on it.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1116
STRING: Now if only the clouds had disappeared somewhere, it
would have been a beautiful day.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x112c
STRING: For just an instant, I recalled the nostalgic color of the
sky where Arie lived.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x117e
STRING: [Fal] “Huh?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1194
STRING: [Chris] “Hm?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x11aa
STRING: I glanced at Fal, who had turned about and looked like
she was waiting for someone to come.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x11dc
STRING: [Fal] “Asino!”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x11f2
STRING: [Chris] “Did you just say Asino?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1208
STRING: The figure she was looking at came within sight, and it
was indeed the person that she had thought it was.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1242
STRING: [Asino] “Hey, Chris.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1258
STRING: [Chris] “Hey. Wait, Asino, don't try and tell me you've

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1294
STRING: [Asino] “What... Is that a way to speak to a friend?

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x12c2
STRING: Ngghh!”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x12ce
STRING: Asino, who had come to a halt in front of me, stumbled

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1300
STRING: [Asino] “Oh, I'm sorry for suddenly stopping like that.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x131e
STRING: [Schoolgirl] “Oh, uh, it's okay.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x133c
STRING: [Fal] “Good afternoon.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x135a
STRING: [Schoolgirl] “Ah, hello, Fal.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x138c
STRING: [Asino] “Hey, Fal.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x13a2
STRING: [Chris] “Does everyone know each other...?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x13b8
STRING: Running into different groups of friends in the one place
was surprising, or should I say...

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x13ce
STRING: Nope, it was just really surprising.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x13e2
STRING: [Fal] “Yes, she and I are both in the vocal course, after

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x13f8
STRING: [Chris] “I see. So that means... Asino, you really were
practicing today, weren't you?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1434
STRING: [Asino] “Stop saying it like it's such a rare thing... You're

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1454
STRING: [Chris] “Alright. So, you know Fal as well?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1486
STRING: [Asino] “Well, it's more like...

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x14b4
STRING: There probably isn't anyone
who doesn't know her, she used to be the class
president.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x14e6
STRING: [Fal] “There was one guy who didn't know my name,

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x14fc
STRING: Chuckling to herself, Fal looked right at me.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1524
STRING: [Asino] “Oh really? I'd love to see that guys face.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1556
STRING: [Fal] “Here you go.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x156e
STRING: While saying so, Fal turned Asino's head to face me.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1584
STRING: [Chris] “Wait...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x15b6
STRING: [Asino] “Seriously?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x15cc
STRING: [Chris] “It's not what you think!”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x15ea
STRING: [Asino] “I haven't said anything yet. Besides, it's totally

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1608
STRING: [Schoolgirl] “Um... Sorry?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x163a
STRING: [Asino] “Oh, my bad! I got distracted by my weird friend

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1650
STRING: [Chris] “Hey, I don't think I said anything weird.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x166e
STRING: [Schoolgirl] “I-I see. So, um...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x16a0
STRING: [Asino] “Right, I was going to walk you home, huh?

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x16ce
STRING: Sorry, I'm gonna head home with him.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x16e4
STRING: [Chris] “Hm...?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x16fa
STRING: The moment he said that, the girl made a distressed
face and looked at me.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1710
STRING: He'd promised to walk her home, but...

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x171c
STRING: [Chris] “Hey...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x174e
STRING: [Fal] “Asino.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1780
STRING: [Asino] “Hm?

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x17ae
STRING: Ah, yes!”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x17ba
STRING: Asino responded to Fal's polite tone of voice almost as

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x17ec
STRING: [Fal] “You made a promise, so you shouldn't say such
things.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1828
STRING: [Asino] “Uh... Umm.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1846
STRING: [Schoolgirl] “Oh, no, it's okay, I didn't mean...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1878
STRING: [Asino] “Yeah... Uh, I'm sorry. I'll walk you.”

STRING: Suddenly changing his previously indifferent attitude, he
turned to face her and spoke in a gentle tone.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x18b6
STRING: [Asino] “Where do you live, again?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x18d4
STRING: [Schoolgirl] “In the New District.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x18f2
STRING: [Asino] “Got it. Shall we go, then?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1910
STRING: [Schoolgirl] “Sure!”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x192e
STRING: [Asino] “Well then, Chris, Fal, I'll see you round.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1960
STRING: [Fal] “Sure. Take care.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1976
STRING: [Chris] “See you...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x19a4
STRING: I was slightly impressed that Asino had been practicing
more than I had expected him to.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x19ba
STRING: Judging by that girls attitude just now, I suppose today
was their first time to practice, so perhaps he'd just
been repeating this kind of thing.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x19da
STRING: He was quite popular, so he was probably taking a laid
back approach to all of this.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x19f0
STRING: [Chris] “...He can really push it sometimes.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1a2a
STRING: [Fal] “Having said that, you don't seem too angry,
though?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1a40
STRING: [Chris] “That's because he's always like that.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1a56
STRING: I only just realized that Fal had stopped speaking in her
polite tone, and had returned to her usual speaking
style.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1a88
STRING: [Fal] “You two are good friends, aren't you?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1a9e
STRING: [Chris] “I guess so... But I have to say, I'm impressed
that you made him obey you like that.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1ada
STRING: [Fal] “What do you mean?

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1b08
STRING: All I did was say that he
shouldn't act in such a way, you know?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1b1e
STRING: [Chris] “I'd say this includes Ms. Cordell, but I think
Asino can't say no to people who use that tone.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1b5a
STRING: [Fal] “Oh, I see.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1b70
STRING: Fal smiled happily and started to walk again.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1bb0
STRING: [Chris] “So, I guess this is where we say bye?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1bea
STRING: [Fal] “I suppose so.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1c18
STRING: Ah...

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1c3c
STRING: But before that, can I ask you
one thing?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1c48
STRING: [Chris] “Hm?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1c7a
STRING: [Fal] “How do you plan to spend Natale?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1c90
STRING: [Chris] “Uh...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1ca6
STRING: I was stuck for words...

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1cb2
STRING: I had no plans.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1cbe
STRING: And I knew that Arie wasn't going to come visit.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1cca
STRING: But, what of it?

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1cd6
STRING: Arie and I were a couple, but that had nothing to do
with whether we were going to spend Natale together
or not.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1cec
STRING: If I answered that I had no plans, Fal might have invited
me to do something.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1d02
STRING: Would it have been better for me to say that I had
plans, so that I wouldn't have to say no to her?

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1d18
STRING: But, it was also possible that I was just being overly self
conscious, and that she was just asking me out of plain
interest.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1d4a
STRING: [Fal] “Is something wrong?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1d60
STRING: [Chris] “It's nothing...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1d92
STRING: [Fal] “I was just thinking that I would like to get some
practice in during Natale...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1da8
STRING: [Chris] “Huh? You want to practice...?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1dda
STRING: [Fal] “Weren't you taught that if you don't use your

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1dfa
STRING: [Chris] “I think I was taught that, yeah...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1e2c
STRING: [Fal] “Were you planning to go out and have fun the

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1e42
STRING: [Chris] “No, of course not!”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1e74
STRING: [Fal] “Ah, but you have already plans?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1e8a
STRING: [Chris] “No... Not particularly.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1ebc
STRING: [Fal] “So, umm...

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1eea
STRING: What will it be?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1ef6
STRING: Oh crap... It was too late to even regret it now.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1f02
STRING: I spoke the words, and again she asked a question I
couldn't get out of answering.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1f18
STRING: [Chris] “Umm...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1f4a
STRING: [Fal] “Ah, I'm sorry, forget about it.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1f60
STRING: [Chris] “R-Really...?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1f92
STRING: [Fal] “No, don't actually forget about it.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1fc0
STRING: Umm...

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1fe4
STRING: Just wait
a moment.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1ff0
STRING: [Chris] “If you want me to wait, I'll wait, but...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x2006
STRING: Fal's cheeks had turned red, and she had to take a few
deep breaths to calm down before she started speaking
again.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x2038
STRING: [Fal] “I guess it's hard to respond to a sudden invitation
like this, right?

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x2070
STRING: You might have plans,

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x2094
STRING: and even if
you don't, you might have some in the future.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x20aa
STRING: I had told her that I didn't have any plans, and I doubted
I would make any.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x20dc
STRING: [Fal] “And I guess it must be a burden for you to
practice so much if we haven't decided to be partners,
right?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x20fc
STRING: And I doubted that practicing with her would be a
burden of any kind...

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x2108
STRING: But, before I could respond by saying so, she had
finished saying what she wanted to say.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x2130
STRING: [Fal] “So um, I was thinking that if you were thinking of
